                        <h5>52 000 SEK/month â†’ 56 000 SEK/month</h5>
                        <h5>~85 000 SEK/yearly bonus</h5>

                        <p>
                            One of my consultant colleagues from Ericsson got word that I would be unemployed soon, so she referred me to her manager. Everything clicked, and I got a huge salary increase.
