                        <p>
                            I spent two and a half years ensuring I worked to deserve the money. I implemented the <a href="/work/trioptima.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TriOptima Design System</a> both in Sketch and code, and even worked closely with the different product teams to create new features and improve the user experience for our customers.
                        </p>

                        <p>
