                        </p>

                        <p>
                            To this day, I don't know if I was gaslighted into cutting my salary by 11 000 SEK to do the same job in a different office with new people or if I misunderstood what they said during the interviews.
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            Here's what I do know. I was not ready to be a Design Leader and let my frustration and hubris get the best of me.
