                    <time>2019</time>

                    <div>
                        <h4>Product Designer</h4>
                        <h5>45 000 SEK/month</h5>
                        <h5>Occupational pension and stock options</h5>

                        <p>
                            With my belly full of humble pie, I joined a great team of experienced individuals at Stravito.
